	<header class="page-header">
				<h2 class="title-secondary">Careers</h2>
				<h1 class="title-primary">
							Working at Citadel					</h1>
								
				<h3 class="header-text">Every day is rich with possibilities.</h3>
						</header>
			<article class="col-main content">
			<p>At Citadel, each team member brings something significant to the table. It is an entrepreneurial environment that inspires strong ideas, healthy debate and constant collaboration. Together, we work to create new frontiers in the investment world.</p>
		</article>
	</section>
<section class="carousel loading" data-script="carousel"><div class="slide slide-1">

	<div class="slide-image">
		<img width="960" height="400" src="//www.citadel.com/_files/uploads/2013/06/careers-working-at-citadel-steve-atkinson.jpg" class="attachment-full" alt="careers-working-at-citadel-steve-atkinson" />	</div>
			<div class="slide-content">
			<div class="text-size-small">
							<blockquote>
					<p>People who come to Citadel know that it is a very robust organization that aggressively invests in the future. This focus on the long term is reassuring.</p>
					<strong class="author">Steve Atkinson</strong><span class="author-title">Chief Operating Officer, Citadel Europe</span>
				</blockquote>
									</div>
